org.simpleframework.http

Interface Method


  • public interface Method
    The Method interface contains the common HTTP methods that are sent with a request. This only contains those methods that have been defined within the RFC 2616 specification. These are defined here for convenience and informational purposes.
    Author:
    Niall Gallagher

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description

      For use with a proxy that can dynamically switch to being a tunnel.

      static java.lang.String OPTIONS
      Represents a request for the communication options available.

      static java.lang.String PUT

      static java.lang.String TRACE
      Invoke a remote application layer loop back of the request.
